@Node snaphistory "SnapShot Manual"
@Next "aboutsafe"
@Prev "attention"
@Toc "Main"
SNAPSHOT HISTORY:


   SnapShot V1.0     V1.0 was never released.


   SnapShot V2.0     Released 03-Jan-93.


   SnapShot V2.2     Bugfix by Bjorn Reese, SHI (Feb-94)

                     Option -v is only valid under the Old File System, if
                     New File Systems is used, this option is ignored. No
                     guru in the script.

   SnapShot V2.3   * Compiled with SAS/C 6.50.

                   * Incorrect exit on failure fixed.

                   * Now correctly counts the number of bytes in a 
                     directory.

                   * You can now also be informed of differences in Devs:
                     and user-startup. Update by Martin Wulffeld/SHI.

                   * Removed some enforcer hits (bugs). Thanks to Alex
                     Holst "Programmers Resort" BBS, Denmark for his
                     excellent help.

                   * Add "Automatic BBS virus test" chapture for BBS users
                     concerning the using of the excellent "Reminder 
                     (timer) program" together with SnapShot. Thanks to
                     Alex Holst "Programmers Resort" BBS for his
                     excellent help.

                   * Added "A quick how to do introduction" chapture for
                     BBS users. Thanks to Alex Holst again.
@Endnode


