                     If  you  know a virus programmer you can get a reward
                     of  $ 5000  for  supplying his name and address.  The
                     fact  is  that  the  law  punishes  data  crime  very
                     severely.  (5 years in jail in most countries).

                     We  are  an  international  group  with more than 600
                     members who have started trying to stop the spread of
                     virus.  Let me give you some example:


